{"tid":2298872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應是否禁止公園「廣場舞」 陳肇始稱主要針對室內場所的「跳老舞」","createTime":"2020-11-24T10:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T12:37:01.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c846596306de5ac72b776f1b06a52315970d7904","tid":2298872,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:51:15.000Z","msg":"回應是否禁止市民公園跳舞 陳肇始稱主要針對室內場所<br />\n<br />\n新型肺炎「歌舞群組」確診個案增至187人，政府宣布禁止食肆及會址跳舞及現場表演，至於其他毋須領牌的場所，是否同樣禁止跳舞活動。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始說，網上流傳影片，一些跳舞活動涉及多人聚集、身體接觸、無戴口罩，導致群組爆發，指有關活動高危，無論場所有牌或無牌，也要全部停止這些高危活動。<br />\n<br />\n被追問如果有關場所毋須領牌，政府如何規管，陳肇始反問是否樣樣都有法例，目前部分處所可能沒有牌照或法例規管，但大家看到現時疫情，希望社會留意所有高風險活動，減少不必要聚集及不戴口罩的活動，期望社會同心抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n至於市民在公園的跳舞是否被禁止，陳肇始提到，禁止在場地內現場表演或跳舞的規定，主要是針對室內場所。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561684-20201124.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561684-20201124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=3ec3d321\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561684-20201124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1166d8ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561684-20201124.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"68a11727a87f334708630175a7a88c444310320c","tid":2298872,"uid":238415,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:52:50.000Z","msg":"乜室外唔係高危過室內架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n龍門又改左位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b2d9efa83e2a825d55a28eafc4f74a0fa1cc8c","tid":2298872,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:53:42.000Z","msg":"就嚟所有室內室外活動都被政府ban 晒啦"},{"pid":"82ab63aac027024fdebf1ee045e121b7bd6c63e8","tid":2298872,"uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68a11727a87f334708630175a7a88c444310320c","tid":2298872,"uid":238415,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:52:50.000Z","msg":"乜室外唔係高危過室內架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n龍門又改左位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:54:06.000Z","msg":"成熟一項，推出一項"},{"pid":"e9025b7aca3ab901d21b61b16e36c70c4a727e66","tid":2298872,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2181acf3e13ddfc7c0ed749140212e847ffe74e","tid":2298872,"uid":276273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:32:05.000Z","msg":"香港有錢闊太都不如無錢既支那大媽，<br />\n大媽有特權跳佢老舞，闊太乜柒都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715aa6a7ef13f9ad7c84ad0223b5dbc1e69abfee","tid":2298872,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:37:01.000Z","msg":"好快就會有回馬槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}